<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Aw Ka Hun Phal Puou</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nunnawpna hun kum deihum
 Zamuol na liem ding chu
 Suihlung khuombang ka gelin
 Suihlung na suhel ngei
 Sim lei namtin vawn chawihte
 Nunnuoma ka lennau
 Zamuolpi na liem ding chu
 Aw ka hun phal puou

[V2]
 2. Na vangletna zal zoin
 Nunnuom in ka leng ui
 Thiemna, chitna, nek leh chak
 Na vangsakna ka muu
 Chung Pathien phatna zalin
 Seino guol haw cheng tawh,
 Chang bang dama nunuom in
 Na sung ka leng ui.

[V3]
 3. Kumsul vei, aw nang hun pha,
 Khangthak guolte pienna;
 Chung Pathien vangsakna thil,
 Go deihum ka chan nau,
 Za muolpi na liem ding chu.
 Bangma'n nang thei puontin;
 Chang bang damin chieh ta'n la,
 Zal mangpha manin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>270</hymn_number>
<author>K. Thuomngell, Tune:S.S 976</author>
</song>